459	\end{theorem}
460	
461	\begin{remark}
462	  On a proper geometrically connected curve, Stein factorization gives $\Gamma(C, \mathcal O_C) = k$, which is finite-dimensional over $k$. Thus the wholespace carrier is producible, unlike the affine-quantified version.
463	\end{remark}
